Jun!

25
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,430
Mr. Jun.

26
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,400
Jun.

27
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,120
Mrs. Jun.

28
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:10,150
Mr. Qi.

29
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:12,150
Madam.

30
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,750
