- Wake up.

33
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:18,150
Madam. Madam.

34
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:18,990
Princess.

35
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:20,310
Xinglan.

36
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:21,470
What happened?

37
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:22,750
What's wrong, Madam?

38
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:23,990
Xinglan.

39
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:28,590
Jun...

40
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:29,990
