41
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,360
Mr. Jun?

42
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:50,030
What about the others?

43
00:02:51,030 --> 00:02:52,910
Everyone else is fine,

44
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:53,750
but...

45
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,710
Mr. Jun...

46
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,570
What's wrong with him?

47
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,360
My Lord.

48
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,100
Everyone's wine was poisoned,

49
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:06,150
but the poison in Mr. Jun's cup
was the strongest.

50
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,710
I'm sorry for your loss.

51
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,870
My loss?

52
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:20,870
Suppress the news.

53
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,520
Find out who the poisoner is.

54
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:24,710
Yes.

55
00:03:27,110 --> 00:03:28,270
Leave.

56
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:32,810
Get out!

57
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:48,430
My Jun.

58
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:53,800
Jun.

59
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,430
(Xinglan.)

60
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:14,560
(There's something I must do.)

61
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,480
(This time it's too dangerous.)

62
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:19,920
(I don't want you to get involved.)

63
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:35,420
(Funeral)

64
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,880
Madam.

65
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:59,260
(Spirit Tablet
of the Late Husband Yuwen Jun)

66
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:05,600
Mrs. Jun,

67
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:08,030
