since Mr. Jun passed away.

68
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:09,720
According to the mansion's rules,

69
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,270
he should be buried as soon as possible.

70
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,120
Everyone, leave.

71
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,750
Madam, bear your grief.

72
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,630
Mr. Jun has been deceased
for seven days.

73
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,160
According to the mansion's rules,

74
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,800
(Spirit Tablet)
let them take the coffin

75
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,160
and bury him in peace.

76
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,510
- Madam.
- Leave.

77
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,240
Anyone who dares to take him away

78
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:32,310
will have to step over my dead body.

79
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,680
We are just...

80
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,390
I told you to leave. Did you hear me?

81
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,110
Yes.

82
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,680
Close the gates.

83
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,120
I won't allow anyone to disturb him.

84
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:49,670
Yes.

85
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:08,620
(Spirit Tablet
of the Late Husband Yuwen Jun)

86
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,700
(Arrangement Office)

87
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:16,950
Have you heard?

88
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,270
It turns out Mr. Jun

89
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:20,040
is our city's Chief Inspector.

90
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,600
