93
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:27,270
He's been planning
to be the future City Lord.

94
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:28,270
You can't say that.

95
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:31,050
Everyone's talking about it in the city.

96
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:34,360
Hasn't the City Lord ordered
to suppress the news?

97
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:35,800
News always gets out.

98
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:39,270
- Let's go.
- Go.

99
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,080
Come on.

100
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:45,880
What's going on?

101
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:46,910
Do you know?

102
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,870
It turns out Mr. Jun

103
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:48,920
was killed by Mr. Yan.

104
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,230
No way.

105
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,120
How could that be?

106
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:52,960
I heard it.

107
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,390
Mr. Jun is the firstborn.

108
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:56,430
He was supposed to be
the City Lord's heir.

109
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,750
But Mr. Yan thinks

110
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:58,960
he's more suitable

111
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,540
than Mr. Jun for that position.

112
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:02,390
Miss Xu is also a foreign assassin.

113
00:07:02,390 --> 00:07:03,920
Mr. Yan has been hiding her here.

114
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:06,160
The two conspired to seize
the position of City Lord.

115
00:07:06,290 --> 00:07:08,870
No wonder everyone says Miss Xu
has an unclear background.

116
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,600
Miss Shen.

117
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,000
Have you finished your work?

118
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,160
Miss Xu is still unconscious
from the poison.

119
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,870
Everyone must remain calm

120
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,240
and not gossip recklessly.

121
00:07:21,190 --> 00:07:23,160
Fortunately,
I was the only one who heard it.

122
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,390
If it were someone else,

123
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:26,170
how many heads
would be enough to chop off?

124
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,190
Miss Shen, thanks for the reminder.

125
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,310
We will remember it.

126
00:07:37,380 --> 00:07:38,270
Let me tell you.

127
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,040
This is outrageous.

128
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:42,870
Say that again.

129
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,870
This is called Fairy Flower.

130
00:07:45,090 --> 00:07:46,750
It was found in Mr. Jun's room.

131
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,440
If kept in the room for fifteen days,

132
00:07:48,450 --> 00:07:49,560
it'd be poisonous.

133
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:52,010
If this flower is ground into powder
and mixed into wine,

134
00:07:52,010 --> 00:07:53,250
it will lead to immediate death.

135
00:07:53,470 --> 00:07:54,700
The physician has confirmed

136
00:07:54,850 --> 00:07:57,420
that the poison that killed Mr. Jun
came from this.

137
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:02,990
This flower?

138
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:06,300
It was a gift from Mr. Yan to Mr. Jun.

139
00:08:06,300 --> 00:08:08,270
All the servants in Junling Pavilion
can prove it.

140
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:09,230
That's impossible.

141
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:11,160
They've always been
on good terms.

142
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:13,240
